			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1. Use Debug Book - Set Quest Flags - Act 2 - GLO - Lifting the curse - Quest States  - Halsin at camp with Spirit\r\n2. Use Debug Book - Set Quest Flags - Act 2 - GLO - Lifting the curse - Quest States - Oliver Fled to Town - teleports Oliver to the plaza in the Town and readies him for a fight. Also teleports you to the plaza as well, you'll only need to approach Oliver to start combat.\r\n3. Attack the Nightdome and reduce its HP to less than 75%."
				},
